    "name": "Startling Appearance",
    "prerequisite": "*Vigilante Dedication*",
    "requirement": "You are unnoticed by the target creature.",
    "subtype": "feat",
    "text": "You can startle foes who are unaware of your presence. Make a Strike against your target. That creature is off-guard against this Strike, as normal. If your Strike hits, the target remains off-guard for the rest of your turn and is frightened 1 (frightened 2 on a critical hit).",
